display="inline"><![CDATA[b^\sharp  \colon  \mathchoice {\textstyle \prod _{  \mathopen {}\left \lparen x\colon \mathsf {toProp}\,A\right \rparen \mathclose {} }}{\textstyle \prod _{  \mathopen {}\left \lparen x\colon \mathsf {toProp}\,A\right \rparen \mathclose {} }}{\scriptstyle \prod _{  \mathopen {}\left \lparen x\colon \mathsf {toProp}\,A\right \rparen \mathclose {} }}{\scriptscriptstyle \prod _{  \mathopen {}\left \lparen x\colon \mathsf {toProp}\,A\right \rparen \mathclose {} }} Bx]]></fr:tex>.</fr:p><fr:p>When we have an element of <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[\mathsf {toProp}\,A]]></fr:tex>, we will say that <fr:tex
